In addition to smithing, high elves are able to fashion 6 unique robes that can be worn by all INT casters of every race. While subcombines for these can be performed by others, the final robe combine must be performed by a high elf. The no drop fierdal robe pattern is available to high elves by telling Chenori Berinal at -14, -260 in North Felwithe "I need a robe pattern". This lady is smart enough to see through illusion, and she won't give the pattern to anyone but a true high elf. She also sells the two recipe books for these robes.<p><br><div align="right">Last Modified By: Niami Denmother&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-05-19 06:41:10&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
